This is a minimal implementation of
. It has been stripped to the bare essentials necessary for doing inference, and converted to PyTorch. The only third party dependencies are

to install dependencies and download pretrained models. In the bash script, GitHub LFS is used to download the VQGan detokenizer and the Weight & Biases python package is used to download the DALL·E Mini and DALL·E Mega transformer models. These models can also be downloaded manually:
Use the command line python scriptimage_from_text.py to generate images. Here are some examples:
python image_from_text.py --text='a comfy chair that looks like an avocado' --mega --seed=4
python image_from_text.py --text='court sketch of godzilla on trial' --mega --seed=100
